ttribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δέκομε Λαί\n                    λει Μέγα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Δέκομε\">ΔΕΚΟΜΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Λαί\n                    λει\">ΛΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΛΕΙ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Μέγα\">ΜΕΓΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΧΑΙΡΕ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic02952_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\" src=\"ISic02952_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002952.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\" src=\"ISic002952-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002952_detail_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\" src=\"ISic002952_detail_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002952_detail.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\" src=\"ISic002952_detail-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002952_r3q_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\" src=\"ISic002952_r3q_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002952_r3q.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\" src=\"ISic002952_r3q-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Dekomos Lailios Mega, farewell!\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text offers a Greek transliteration of the Latin names Decimus Laelius, and either a translation of Magnus, or simply transcription of the Greek 'Mega'. Manganaro suggested this might be a libertus of Decimus Laelius, the friend of Pompeius Magnus, ftribune of 54 BC.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 58.1045 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 36.0847 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1965 201 tav. 72.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1974 131 n. 68 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002336\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002336\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1979 16 tav. 1.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002685\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002685\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1987 210 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001552\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001552\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1991 92 fig. 105 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001550\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001550\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1993 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.or