},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Dekomos Lailios Mega, farewell!\u003C/p>  ",{"id":323,"html":324},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text offers a Greek transliteration of the Latin names Decimus Laelius, and either a translation of Magnus, or simply transcription of the Greek 'Mega'. Manganaro suggested this might be a libertus of Decimus Laelius, the friend of Pompeius Magnus, ftribune of 54 BC.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":326,"html":327},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 58.1045 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 36.0847 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1965 201 tav. 72.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1974 131 n. 68 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002336\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002336\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1979 16 tav. 1.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002685\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002685\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1987 210 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001552\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001552\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1991 92 fig. 105 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001550\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001550\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1993 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001548\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001548\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Tullio 1994 65-67 fig. 52 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002387\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002387\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 2005 849 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002116\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002116\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Montalbano 2008 176 VS 3 tav. 33.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001740\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001740\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":329,"html":330},"handnote"," Line 1-3  70-80  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":332,"html":333},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[335,337,340,341],{"html":336},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag",{"id":338,"lang":137,"html":339},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δέκομε Λαί\n                    λει Μέγα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Δέκομε\">Δέκομε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Λαί\n                    λει\">Λαί-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>λει\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Μέγα\">Μέγα\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>χαῖρε \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":336},{"id":342,"lang":137,"html":343},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!