   \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic02952_tiled.tif\" height=\"3385px\" width=\"3808px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic002952.jpg\" height=\"3385px\" width=\"3808px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic002952_detail_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic002952_detail.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic002952_r3q_tiled.tif\" height=\"3454px\" width=\"2925px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic002952_r3q.jpg\" height=\"3454px\" width=\"2925px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Mandralisca\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"praenomen\">Δέκομε\u003C/name> \u003Cname type=\"nomen\">Λαί\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\" break=\"no\"/>λει\u003C/name> \u003Cname type=\"cognomen\">Μέγα\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>χαῖρε\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--external apparatus criticus (if applicable)-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Dekomos Lailios Mega, farewell!\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>The text offers a Greek transliteration of the Latin names Decimus Laelius, and either a translation of Magnus, or simply transcription of the Greek 'Mega'.  Manganaro suggested this might be a libertus of Decimus Laelius, the friend of Pompeius Magnus, ftribune of 54 BC.\u003C/p>\n                    \u003C!--85 x 74 x 15 cm. Block of limestone. Letters 7/8 cm high, 'forse del I sec. a.C.' (Manganaro). Reads: Dekome Lailei Mega chaire. M comments thai it is an interesting example of greek transcription, of 'Decimus Laeilius Magnus. Observes poss. that this a libertus of Decimus Laelius, friend of Pompey (RE n.6; tr.pl. 54 BC; no assigned quaestorship); for more poss. links, see M's note, p.201 n.83). Tullio 1979 writes: 'Si tratta di un reperto particolarmente importante, non solo per la testimonianza storico-linguistica in se stessa, ma anche per la funzione che, grazie all'anlogia con i blocchi venuti alla luce durante i recenti scavi sistematici della Necropoli di Cefalu, e possible riconoscergli e cioe quella di segnacolo di una tomba 'monumentale' ad enchytrismos.'  Whatever T's issues with the text, earlier, in 1991, he simply adopts that of Manganaro: Dekome Lailei Mega chaire. In 1991, he writes: 'La lingua adottata (greco) ed il nome del personaggio, che va ricollegato alla presenza di cives romani a Cefalu, propone una problematica sociologica di un certo interesse'. Cf. similar names at Lilyabaeum?-->\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>58.1045\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>36.0847\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1965\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>201 tav. 72.2\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RGTHAFKT\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tullio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1974\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>131 n. 68\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/QRB9I8X3\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002336\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002336\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tullio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1979\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>16 tav. 1.2\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/NK6RHMIX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002685\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002685\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tullio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1987\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>210\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/PE7MRIXU\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001552\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001552\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tullio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1991\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>92 fig. 105\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/9FVDG22E\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001550\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001550\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tullio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1993\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange/>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/PS8GH694\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001548\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001548\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tullio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1994\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>65-67 fig. 52\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RUZQ9EVS\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002387\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002387\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cau